ll|title=John Wick 2 Filming Begins This Fall!|publisher=Coming Soon|last=Lesnick|first=Silas|date=2015-09-22|access-date=2015-11-11|archive-date=2020-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120082859/https://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/615917-john-wick-2-filming-begins-this-fall|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://collider.com/john-wick-2-director-is-chad-stahelski/|title=Exclusive: Chad Stahelski To Direct ‘John Wick 2’ Solo|publisher=Collider|last=Wwintraub|first=Steven|date=2015-09-24|access-date=2015-11-11|archive-date=2015-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151027160246/http://collider.com/john-wick-2-director-is-chad-stahelski/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://collider.com/john-wick-2-story-details-action-scenes-keanu-reeves/|title=Exclusive: ‘John Wick 2′ Story Details Revealed|publisher=Collider|last=Foutch|first=Haleigh|date=2015-10-05|access-date=2015-11-11|archive-date=2015-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151031211914/http://collider.com/john-wick-2-story-details-action-scenes-keanu-reeves/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年10月，歌手兼演員的[[凡夫俗子_(歌手)|凡夫俗子]]加入劇組飾演女性犯罪組織的領導者<ref name="CommonCast">{{cite news|last1=Kit|first1=Borys|title=Common to Play Villain in Keanu Reeves' 'John Wick 2' (Exclusive)|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/john-wick-2-common-play-834635|accessdate=2015-10-27|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2015-10-26|archive-date=2019-07-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190726195634/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/john-wick-2-common-play-834635|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而[[伊恩·麥克夏恩|伊恩·麥克夏恩]]確認回歸本集繼續詮釋大陸飯店的神秘主人溫斯頓<ref name="McShaneCast">{{cite news|last1=Kit|first1=Borys|title=Ian McShane Returns for Keanu Reeves' 'John Wick 2' (Exclusive)|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/keanu-reeves-john-wick-2-834725|accessdate=2015-10-27|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2015-10-26|archive-date=2017-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171030090216/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/keanu-reeves-john-wick-2-834725|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年11月，[[布麗姬·穆娜|布麗姬·穆娜]]、[[約翰·拉奎查莫|約翰·拉奎查莫]]、[[湯瑪斯·薩多斯基|湯瑪斯·薩多斯基]]和[[藍斯·瑞迪克|藍斯·瑞迪克]]被證實再次回歸飾演自己在前集的角色，而新加入的演員包括[[露比·蘿絲|露比·蘿絲]]、[[里卡多·史卡馬西奧|里卡多·史卡馬西奧]]與[[彼得·史托馬|彼得·史托馬]]<ref name="NovemberCast">{{cite news|last1=Jaafar|first1=Ali|title='John Wick 2' Fills Out Cast, Old Favorites Return|url=http://deadline.com/2015/11/john-wicks-2-keanu-reeves-ian-mcshane-common-lionsgate-summit-basil-iwanyk-1201615113/|accessdate=2015-11-09|publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline]]|date=2015-11-09|archive-date=2019-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190626223912/https://deadline.com/2015/11/john-wicks-2-keanu-reeves-ian-mcshane-common-lionsgate-summit-basil-iwanyk-1201615113/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年12月，宣布[[勞倫斯·費許朋|勞倫斯·費許朋]]也於片中參演<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/laurence-fishburne-keanu-reeves-john-wick-2-1201664624/|title=Laurence Fishburne Reunites With Keanu Reeves for ‘John Wick 2’ Cameo|last=McNary|first=Dave|date=2015-12-18|access-date=2016-08-03|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108130313/https://variety.com/2015/film/news/laurence-fishburne-keanu-reeves-john-wick-2-1201664624/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 拍攝 ===
電影正式於2015年10月26日在[[紐約市|紐約市]]開拍<ref>{{cite news|title=On the Set for 10/30/15: Keanu Reeves Starts on John Wick Sequel, Seth Rogen and Zac Efron Wrap Up Neighbors 2|url=http://www.ssninsider.com/on-the-set-for-103015-keanu-reeves-starts-on-john-wick-sequel-seth-rogen-and-zac-efron-wrap-up-neighbors-2/|accessdate=2015-11-02|work=SSN Insider|date=2015-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151101015915/http://www.ssninsider.com/on-the-set-for-103015-keanu-reeves-starts-on-john-wick-sequel-seth-rogen-and-zac-efron-wrap-up-neighbors-2/|archive-date=2015-11-01|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。拍攝的第一週結束前，也在[[曼哈頓|曼哈頓]]進行過<ref>{{cite news|title=Keanu Reeves has bloody cuts on face as he takes on foes in dramatic scenes while filming John Wick 2|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-3298222/Keanu-Reeves-bloody-cuts-face-takes-foes-dramatic-scenes-filming-John-Wick-2.html|accessdate=2015-11-02|work=[[The_Daily_Mail|The Daily Mail]]|date=2015-10-31|archive-date=2016-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160402013941/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-3298222/Keanu-Reeves-bloody-cuts-face-takes-foes-dramatic-scenes-filming-John-Wick-2.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其他取景地包括[[義大利|義大利]]<ref name="McShaneCast" />。

== 發行 ==
電影由[[頂峰娛樂|頂峰娛樂]]定於2017年2月10日在美國上映<ref>{{cite news|last1=Evry|first1=Max|title=John Wick: Chapter Two Gets a Release Date|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/658353-john-wick-chapter-two-gets-a-release-date#/slide/1|accessdate=2016-02-18|publisher=Comingsoon.net|date=2016-02-18|archive-date=2019-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190815190016/https://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/658353-john-wick-chapter-two-gets-a-release-date#/slide/1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。並於2017年1月30日在位於[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]的{{link-en|聚光燈好萊塢|ArcLight Hollywood}}上首映。

在英國，電影被[[英國電影分級委員會|英國電影分級委員會]]評為15級（15 certificate）<ref name=bbfc>{{cite web | url=http://www.bbfc.co.uk/releases/john-wick-chapter-2-film | title=''John Wick: Chapter 2'' | work=[[British_Board_of_Film_Classification|British Board of Film Classification]] | accessdate=2017-01-27 | archive-date=2019-08-28 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190828064347/https://bbfc.co.uk/releases/john-wick-chapter-2-film | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 評價 ===
《捍衛任務2：殺神回歸》整體獲得的評價以正面居多。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]基於261條評論，持有89%的新鮮度，平均得分7.3／10；該網站共識：「《捍衛任務2：殺神回歸》做到了一部續集應該要有的--在這種情況下，意味著不停加倍、驚人的動作編排，這使與前集相當的樂趣。」<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/john_wick_chapter_2 |title=John Wick: Chapter 2 (2017) |publisher=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2017-02-06 |archive-date=2021-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225220634/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/john_wick_chapter_2 |dead-url=no }}</ref>而在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上則得分75，代表「整體良好的評價」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/john-wick-chapter-2 |title=John Wick: Chapter 2 reviews |publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |accessdate=2017-02-06 |archive-date=2019-08-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190817032440/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/john-wick-chapter-2 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]調查，觀眾的反應在A+至F間落於「A-」<ref name="CinemaScore">{{cite web |url=https://m.cinemascore.com |title=CinemaScore |work=cinemascore.com |access-date=2021-12-18 |archive-date=2015-02-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150217211441/https://m.cinemascore.com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===
在美國和加拿大，《捍衛任務2：殺神回歸》與《[[樂高蝙蝠俠電影|樂高蝙蝠俠電影]]》和《[[格雷的五十道陰影：束縛_(電影)|格雷的五十道陰影：束縛]]》共同上映和競爭，估計能從首週末獲得2000萬美元的票房<ref name="DEADproj">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2017/01/fifty-shades-darker-lego-batman-box-office-projection-1201894855/|title=‘Fifty Shades Darker’ Poised To Submit To ‘Lego Batman’: Pre-Valentine’s Day Weekend B.O. Forecast|author=Anthony D'Alessandro|work=''[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]''|date=2017-01-26|accessdate=2017-01-27|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112042623/https://deadline.com/2017/01/fifty-shades-darker-lego-batman-box-office-projection-1201894855/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=preview>{{cite web |url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2017/01/27/box-office-can-lego-batman-fifty-shades-darker-and-john-wick-outperform-their-tracking/#5c5d0870631f |title=Box Office: Can 'Lego Batman,' 'Fifty Shades Darker' And 'John Wick 2' Outperform Their Tracking? |work=[[Forbes|Forbes]] |access-date=2017-02-02 |archive-date=2017-02-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170220095047/http://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2017/01/27/box-office-can-lego-batman-fifty-shades-darker-and-john-wick-outperform-their-tracking/#5c5d0870631f |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並在2月10日上映首日獲得1100萬美元的佳績，排名第三，而[[奈·沙馬蘭|奈·沙馬蘭]]的《[[分裂_(2016年電影)|分裂]]》則緊追在後。美國首週末票房總計3000萬美元，為前集的首週末票房的兩倍，並位居當週票房排名第三<ref name="weekend">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2017/02/fifty-shades-darker-lego-batman-john-wick-chapter-2-box-office-1201907911/|title=‘Lego Batman’ Hooks $54M+, ‘Fifty Shades’ Rachets Up $48M+, ‘John Wick 2’ Targets $29M+ – Saturday Update|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|access-date=2017-02-13|archive-date=2017-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170220135527/http://deadline.com/2017/02/fifty-shades-darker-lego-batman-john-wick-chapter-2-box-office-1201907911/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

台灣方面，最終票房為新台幣8400萬元<ref>{{cite news |author1=蔡曉松 |title=【重擊報告】2019 年上半年度票房前十名：《復仇者聯盟：終局之戰》以8.9億領先群雄，這份榜單還有什麼端倪？ |url=https://punchline.asia/archives/53902 |work=娛樂重擊 |date=2019-06-14 |accessdate=2019-06-21 |archive-date=2021-01-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124100943/https://punchline.asia/archives/53902 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

